From a sample FHIR record for a patient in MA:

```
        "address": [
          {
            "extension": [
              {
                "url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/geolocation",
                "extension": [
                  {
                    "url": "latitude",
                    "valueDecimal": -71.026717
                  },
                  {
                    "url": "longitude",
                    "valueDecimal": 42.021617
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
```

